org.apache.james.imap.encode.base

Class AbstractChainedImapEncoder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.james.imap.encode.base.AbstractChainedImapEncoder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ImapEncoder
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ACLResponseEncoder, AuthenticateResponseEncoder, CapabilityResponseEncoder, ContinuationResponseEncoder, EnableResponseEncoder, ESearchResponseEncoder, ExistsResponseEncoder, ExpungeResponseEncoder, FetchResponseEncoder, FlagsResponseEncoder, ListResponseEncoder, LSubResponseEncoder, MailboxStatusResponseEncoder, NamespaceResponseEncoder, RecentResponseEncoder, SearchResponseEncoder, StatusResponseEncoder, VanishedResponseEncoder, XListResponseEncoder

    public abstract class AbstractChainedImapEncoder
extends Object
implements ImapEncoder
    Abstract base class for chained ImapEncoder implementations. Implementations of this will check if the ImapMessage should get encoded by this Implementation or should get passed to the next ImapEncoder in the chain
